a29 23

<h2>Equipment Policy for Non-Members</h2>

<p>Non-members are able to rent gear under certain circumstances.  The non-member <i>must</i> be going on a trip with a member.  If a member wishes to get gear for more than just one non-member friend, then the non-member must pay the following rental fees:</p>

<ul>
 <li>Tent 		$5</li>
 <li>Tarp		$1</li>
 <li>Sleeping bag	$4</li>
 <li>Sleeping pad	$1</li>
 <li>Backpack		$3</li>
 <li>Stove (with fuel)	$3</li>
 <li>Pans		$3</li>
 <li>Climbing shoes	$3</li>
 <li>Harness		$3</li>
 <li>ATC and biner	$1</li>
 <li>Chalk bag		$1</li>
 <li>Helmet		$3</li>
 <li>Canoe		$15</li>
 <li>Kayak		$15</li>
 <li>PFD		$4</li>
 <li>Mountain Bike	$5 per day</li>
</ul>
